Companion Normal Mode Active
    Events
        Time - Every 2.00 seconds of game time
    Conditions
        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
            Conditions
                (Number of units in Companion_Group) Greater than 0
                (Number of units in TamedUnits) Greater than 0
    Actions
        -------- ===================================== --------
        -------- FOCUS NAZGREK GROUP --------
        Set VariableSet CompVarPoint = (Position of Nazgrek)
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                (Number of units in CompanionFocusNazgrek) Greater than 0
            Then - Actions
                Unit Group - Pick every unit in CompanionFocusNazgrek and do (Actions)
                    Loop - Actions
                        Set VariableSet CV = (Custom value of (Picked unit))
                        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                            If - Conditions
                                IsUnitAlive[CV] Equal to True
                                UnitIsCasting[CV] Equal to False
                                GCSM_UnitInCombat[CV] Equal to False
                                UnitMoving[CV] Equal to False
                                CompanionUnitIdle[CV] Equal to False
                            Then - Actions
                                Set VariableSet CompVarAngle = (Random angle)
                                Set VariableSet CompVarDistance = (Random real number between 100.00 and 300.00)
                                Set VariableSet CompVarTarget = (CompVarPoint offset by CompVarDistance towards CompVarAngle degrees.)
                                Unit - Order (Picked unit) to Attack-Move To CompVarTarget
                                Custom script:   call RemoveLocation(udg_CompVarTarget)
                            Else - Actions
                                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                                    If - Conditions
                                        IsUnitAlive[CV] Equal to True
                                        UnitIsCasting[CV] Equal to False
                                        (Current order of (Picked unit)) Not equal to (Order(smart))
                                        Or - Any (Conditions) are true
                                            Conditions
                                                GCSM_UnitInCombat[(Custom value of Nazgrek)] Equal to True
                                                (Distance between (Position of (Picked unit)) and (Position of Nazgrek)) Greater than or equal to 600.00
                                    Then - Actions
                                        Unit - Order (Picked unit) to Right-Click Nazgrek
                                    Else - Actions
            Else - Actions
